  <p class=3DMsoNormal><span lang=3DEN-GB style=3D'mso-ansi-language:EN-GB;
  mso-no-proof:yes'>Tyderios is a rare inert gas used in weapons, shielding=
 and
  reactor components.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal><span lang=3DEN-GB style=3D'mso-ansi-language:EN-GB;
  mso-no-proof:yes'>Tyderios gas has a pinkish tinge. It is heavier than ai=
r and
  will sink to ground-level unless buoyed by other surrounding gases. It is
  found in trace quantities at Ice and Frozen Gas Giant worlds and Gas clou=
ds.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal><span lang=3DEN-GB style=3D'mso-ansi-language:EN-GB;
  mso-no-proof:yes'>Occurrence: common</span></p>
